'''Celebration III''' was the third ''[[Star Wars]]'' convention in a [[Celebration|series]] held by [[LucasArts]] to celebrate the [[May 19]], [[2005]] release of [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']].

Over 34,000 fans attended the four-day event, which was held from Thursday, [[April 21]] to Sunday, [[April 24]], 2005 in [[Wikipedia:Indianapolis, Indiana|Indianapolis, Indiana]]. There were many booths with merchandise and displays, and members of the [[501st Legion (fan organization)|501st]] were predominant at the event.

[[George Lucas]] made an appearance on the 23rd, confirming a [[Star Wars: Underworld|''Star Wars'' live-action television series]] and [[Star Tours: The Adventures Continue|Star Tours II]].

